    <item>
      <title>普京与金正恩同意若遭受袭击将立即提供军事援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/putin-kim-agree-to-immediately-offer-military-aid-if-attacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京和朝鲜领导人金正恩同意，如果其中一方受到袭击，将立即提供军事援助，重启冷战时期的一项协议，此举可能会引起美国及其合作伙伴的不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/putin-kim-agree-to-immediately-offer-military-aid-if-attacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 02:17:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国情报机构发现拜登与特朗普的竞争中没有中国青睐者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/china-sees-no-upside-to-biden-or-trump-as-president-us-spies-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国间谍认为，中国领导人认为总统乔·拜登与其前任唐纳德·特朗普之间即将展开的选举对决几乎没有任何好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/china-sees-no-upside-to-biden-or-trump-as-president-us-spies-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁获赦免的前总统藤森重回政坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/peru-s-pardoned-ex-president-fujimori-resurfaces-in-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁前总统阿尔贝托·藤森 (Alberto Fujimori) — 因在行刑队杀戮中所扮演的角色而被判有罪，去年获得赦免 — 现在正式重返政坛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/peru-s-pardoned-ex-president-fujimori-resurfaces-in-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 22:14:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约秘书长斯托尔滕贝格敦促加拿大与盟国一道实现防御目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/nato-chief-stoltenberg-urges-canada-to-join-allies-in-meeting-defense-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格加大对加拿大的压力，要求其履行将 GDP 的 2% 用于国防的承诺，并指出加拿大是今年无法实现这一水平的少数成员国之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/nato-chief-stoltenberg-urges-canada-to-join-allies-in-meeting-defense-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 22:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国瞄准欧洲各地贸易战目标进行反击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/china-eyes-trade-war-targets-across-europe-for-counterstrikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与过去的争端一样，中国似乎准备采取一系列行动，惩罚欧盟对电动汽车征收关税的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/china-eyes-trade-war-targets-across-europe-for-counterstrikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本最具权势女性之争已拉开帷幕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-19/tokyo-governor-s-race-defined-by-two-powerful-women</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京都知事之争将由日本两位最受瞩目的女性政治家决定，但挑战者斋藤莲舫是否有足够的实力推翻小池百合子知事的职位？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-19/tokyo-governor-s-race-defined-by-two-powerful-women</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 21:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大高校限缩措施或将导致赴加留学生数量减半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/college-clampdown-on-track-to-halve-student-arrivals-to-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一家教育招聘公司的分析，加拿大对外国学生计划的改革有望使今年批准的国际学习许可数量减少一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/college-clampdown-on-track-to-halve-student-arrivals-to-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 20:36:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南无视美国批评，向普京致意以加强两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/vietnam-welcomes-putin-in-boost-to-ties-ignoring-us-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南欢迎俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的到访，尽管美国批评克里姆林宫入侵乌克兰，但越南仍强调了与莫斯科数十年来的友好关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/vietnam-welcomes-putin-in-boost-to-ties-ignoring-us-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:11:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平暗示将继续严厉打击军队腐败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/xi-calls-for-greater-loyalty-and-discipline-in-china-s-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国领导人习近平表示，他将推进中国历史上最大规模的反腐风暴之一，并在一次罕见的军队会议上呼吁军队“深刻反思”，以确保军队忠诚卫国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/xi-calls-for-greater-loyalty-and-discipline-in-china-s-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 11:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
